---
/**
 * GPU execution hierarchy: Grid → Blocks → Warps → Threads
 * Animated zoom-in showing the structure.
 */
---

<figure class="gpu-hierarchy">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 680 240" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="img" aria-label="GPU thread hierarchy: Grid contains Blocks, which contain Warps of 32 Threads">
    <!-- Grid -->
    <rect x="10" y="10" width="660" height="220" rx="10" class="grid-box" />
    <text x="340" y="30" class="level-label">Grid (all blocks for this kernel)</text>

    <!-- Blocks -->
    {Array.from({ length: 3 }).map((_, bi) => (
      <g>
        <rect x={25 + bi * 215} y="40" width="200" height="180" rx="8" class="block-box"
              style={`animation-delay: ${0.2 + bi * 0.15}s`} />
        <text x={125 + bi * 215} y="57" class="block-label">{`Block ${bi}`}</text>

        {/* Warps within each block */}
        {Array.from({ length: 3 }).map((_, wi) => (
          <g>
            <rect x={35 + bi * 215} y={65 + wi * 50} width="180" height="42" rx="5" class="warp-box"
                  style={`animation-delay: ${0.5 + bi * 0.15 + wi * 0.1}s`} />
            <text x={45 + bi * 215} y={78 + wi * 50} class="warp-label">{`Warp ${wi} (32 threads)`}</text>

            {/* Threads within each warp */}
            {Array.from({ length: 32 }).map((_, ti) => (
              <rect x={38 + bi * 215 + ti * 5.4} y={83 + wi * 50} width="4" height="18" rx="1"
                    class="thread-box"
                    style={`animation-delay: ${0.8 + bi * 0.1 + wi * 0.08 + ti * 0.01}s`} />
            ))}
          </g>
        ))}
        <text x={125 + bi * 215} y="212" class="dots">⋯ more warps</text>
      </g>
    ))}
  </svg>
  <figcaption>A kernel launch creates a <strong>grid</strong> of <strong>blocks</strong>. Each block contains <strong>warps</strong> of 32 threads that execute in lockstep (SIMT). The GPU schedules warps across its streaming multiprocessors.</figcaption>
</figure>

<style>
  .gpu-hierarchy {
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }
  .gpu-hierarchy svg {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 680px;
    display: block;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .gpu-hierarchy figcaption {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: #888;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }
  .grid-box {
    fill: #fafafa;
    stroke: #bbb;
    stroke-width: 2;
    stroke-dasharray: 8 4;
  }
  .block-box {
    fill: #f0ffe8;
    stroke: #8cc063;
    stroke-width: 1.5;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fade-in 0.4s ease-out forwards;
  }
  .warp-box {
    fill: #eef4ff;
    stroke: #9bb8e8;
    stroke-width: 1;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fade-in 0.3s ease-out forwards;
  }
  .thread-box {
    fill: #7da4d9;
    stroke: none;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fade-in 0.15s ease-out forwards;
  }
  .level-label {
    font-family: 'SF Mono', 'Fira Code', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-anchor: middle;
    fill: #888;
  }
  .block-label {
    font-family: 'SF Mono', 'Fira Code', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-anchor: middle;
    fill: #4a7c2e;
  }
  .warp-label {
    font-family: 'SF Mono', 'Fira Code', monospace;
    font-size: 7.5px;
    font-weight: 600;
    fill: #4a6fa5;
  }
  .dots {
    font-family: 'SF Mono', 'Fira Code', monospace;
    font-size: 8px;
    text-anchor: middle;
    fill: #aaa;
  }
  @keyframes fade-in {
    from { opacity: 0; }
    to { opacity: 1; }
  }
</style>
